    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目前，游戏只包含《Vanova的故事》的第一集。但这只是一个开始……更多章节即将通过免费更新推出！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.poster.avif?t=1747090428\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.webm?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.mp4?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《凡城探案故事》是一款互动冒险游戏，兼具桌游和电子游戏的玩法，适合2至4位玩家参与。喜欢画风个性、色彩绚烂的场景？喜欢跟朋友一齐游戏？喜欢剧情引人入胜的指向点击游戏？那这款游戏绝对不要错过！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/6c8b51bc070e5848ffb1c3cf62639b35.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>欢迎来到凡诺瓦市，欢迎来到这个手绘的世界。无论是2D还是3D视角，你都需要敏锐观察，才能无往不利，循迹而上，破解谜团，惩凶除恶！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/52ff51b76bed35ea17d55c89d21e7a74.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>每到一个地方，你都会遇到性格各异的角色。如果其中有些人不愿意跟你交流，不如……换你队友试试？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/8429f026acf7b2c3cf87983a029134f4.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>有人圆滑老练，有人不怒自威，有人体格壮硕，有人魅力四射——每个侦探都有各自的强项，令他们能够发现不同的线索。每位侦探的经历冒险和对话选项各不相同，因此选择不同的角色会为获得不一样的调查体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/f12d2bc5b6b43d2e655c57e2691c84d9.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>嫌犯拒绝与你对话，而此时你手中证据不足，无法让对方认罪伏法，怎么办？不如把线索交给队友，让他们替你撬开嫌犯的嘴巴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/d269726e510211f9e9ef559c5d27fd86.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>不同的案件需要不同的调查手段。每次调查都会用到新的机制，让你不得不改换调查思路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/652c6cb0693c27adc2f8d0299d566f36.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>觉得自己解开了谜团？那就跟朋友凑在一起，串连线索，推理案情，向老大汇报你们的发现吧。汇报之前，最好确定所有同伴意见达成一致，因为一旦假设不成立，你的损失会非常惨重。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/d46f072e7de590872f8e1788e33ecd36.avif?t=1747090428\" width=622 height=329 /></span></p>",
